# Bioinfo Learning

This repository is my personal bioinformatics learning journey.

## Goals
- Learn Python for biology data analysis
- Understand core bioinformatics concepts
- Build small projects using real biological datasets

## Structure
- week1/: basic Python + intro bioinformatics concepts
- week2/: sequence analysis and data handling
- data/: datasets used in projects

## Tools
- Python
- Jupyter Notebook
- Git & GitHub
